      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six, featuring a 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous induction response. The 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, sending power through a refreshed limited-slip differential. Critical mechanical addressals have been completed, including a comprehensive VANOS service and subframe reinforcement to mitigate chassis fatigue. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative steering and balanced turn-in characteristic of the chassis. A mechanically sound, high-performance machine ready for the enthusiast driver.",
