    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 BMW M240i Coupe, a vehicle that perfectly bridges the gap between daily comfort and exhilarating performance. Finished in Mineral Grey Metallic, the paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scratch near the rear wheel arch\u2014honest signs of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. The interior is a highlight, featuring Oyster Dakota leather that remains supple and free of tears or heavy bolsters wear. It comes fully equipped with the Harman Kardon premium audio system, heated power seats, and an intuitive navigation system, all of which function perfectly. Under the hood, the 3.0L turbocharged inline-six engine runs smoothly, benefiting from a rigorous service history performed exclusively at authorized centers. Most recently, the vehicle underwent a full inspection, oil service, and brake fluid flush. The Michelin Pilot Super Sport tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a non-smoker\u2019s car with a clean title and a comprehensive folder of maintenance receipts, ready for its next owner to drive away with peace of mind.",
